Arnold Lucy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arnold_Lucy 0 Arnold Lucy (born Walter George Campbell, 8 August 1865 – 15 December 1945) was a British theatre and film actor, best known as Professor Kantorek in All Quiet on the Western Front (1930).
